{"tid":2316100,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔請入 否則本人隨時會被取消保釋","createTime":"2020-12-07T15:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T23:30:43.000Z","uid":9919,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"69e74ef37e1bf5a370d2dbd3b2ab60cb2e920a83","tid":2316100,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"今日會員 乃木坂飯 (#81783) 係&quot;荃灣工廈TATP爆炸品案已還押逾16個月盧手足今認罪將會交付高等法院判刑&quot; 既POST入面 <span class=\"red\">曾經引用回覆過我 好記得你上次起連登開po教人整炸彈</span>(圖1)<br />\n<span class=\"red\">本人亦問過佢(乃木坂飯 (#81783))2次 你真係咁記得同肯定無記錯人？(圖2) 及 你真係好記得同肯定無記錯人？</span>(圖2)<br />\n都沒有我到回覆<br />\n然後 亦問過佢(乃木坂飯 (#81783)) <br />\n<span class=\"red\">問左2次無答即係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係鳩up?<br />\n如果我本身有保釋條件係唔可以講關於爆炸品既野而又有moon post狗睇緊亦因為你呢句野搞到我入去荔枝角你係咪會好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>(圖2)<br />\n最終得到既回覆就係<br />\n<span class=\"red\">明架啦<br />\n你叫連仔刪左PO唔通又起度講咩<br />\n你要注意安全呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>(圖3)<br />\n請連仔幫我澄清本人從來無叫過你(連仔)或任何管理員刪除任何關於&quot;教人整炸彈&quot;POST<br />\n本人亦會在上載自己既保釋紙 證明自己係 不准談及/發收爆炸品既資料(圖4)<br />\n <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IKCcMcE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIKCcMcE.png&h=b32da9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pxTotEa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpxTotEa.png&h=66b53b38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1ZZEiV0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1ZZEiV0.png&h=3ab250f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EqGHc8G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEqGHc8G.jpg&h=9c6e638d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"859a0e17f68a2084e086882898f98d559384395e","tid":2316100,"uid":6845,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T15:12:16.000