png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpxTotEa.png&h=66b53b38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1ZZEiV0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1ZZEiV0.png&h=3ab250f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EqGHc8G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEqGHc8G.jpg&h=9c6e638d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:30:04.000Z","msg":"未曾有刪除有關會員愛德華艾力克 #9919 的留言記錄"},{"pid":"3306c6aa0fc4e26b376c42b3dd53cda3bbdc5684","tid":2316100,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"用新act 啦"},{"pid":"4c4e942e8b4724f06a1343b22ed393b16b53b946","tid":2316100,"uid":166149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T16:06:54.000Z","msg":"人無事先可以做世界冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac981cc936641eb3d6e1dcf03077164bd8f34a83","tid":2316100,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3306c6aa0fc4e26b376c42b3dd53cda3bbdc5684","tid":2316100,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"用新act 啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"邊到整個新ac返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4772363cc12cdadfbcbe1d2f8a77eb7895f6bcdd","tid":2316100,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T23:14:47.000Z","msg":"安全至上 ac留黎意義不大 乖乖地聽以上巴打建議好唔好"}],"pinned":{"pid":"76e1c0a209731a226a08229120538046614923b6","tid":2316100,"uid":1,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:30:04.000Z","msg":"未曾有刪除有關會員愛德華艾力克 #9919 的留言記錄"}}